    <h1>Large Language Model (LLM)</h1>
    <p class="description">An AI system trained on massive text data to understand and generate human language. LLMs power <strong>ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overviews</strong> — the AI search tools reshaping how users find your brand online.</p>
